{"tid":941981,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［冇圖］聖誕拒絕左一個靚女嘅要求","createTime":"2018-12-15T09:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T18:18:01.000Z","uid":46881,"like":76,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"512b2fe47455a01842a1d0b1e973de86b5d4be1a","tid":941981,"uid":46881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:29:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱準備行入商場<br />\n見到前面玻璃門有個女仔企在係門口派傳單<br />\n個女仔着住紅色短裙 白色緊身衣 過膝襪好似都幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見佢好似冇乜心機派 <br />\n因為見到佢都冇派俾前面行入去啲人<br />\n咁我行左過去 佢好溫柔咁同我講：拎張睇下丫 先生 <br />\n把聲都幾好聽 幾cute <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後 <br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n我望都冇望佢一眼就行左入商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似佢同我表白之後俾我粒聲唔出拒絕左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個腦就ff左佢望住我行入商場<br />\n之係個玻璃門望住門內我不羈的背影離開嘅畫面<br />\n啊！係 最尾我仲火影跑跑走左去食M記<br />\n一諗起就覺得自己好型 好浪子 <br />\n好似佐助拒絕小櫻咁<br />\n講返都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：第一次拒絕靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba01fe52bb8317fb7029d7fb12331b83f8335e1","tid":941981,"uid":38904,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:31:09.000Z","msg":"條女: 好彩條死毒撚冇攞張嘢咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係嘅話我要去洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9bd483bb875389f5a2aad46e067cecc485946a","tid":941981,"uid":50328,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30dcf8655e6e178937ebaad7cbd1801f5450294f","tid":941981,"uid":46881,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9d9bd483bb875389f5a2aad46e067cecc485946a","tid":941981,"uid":50328,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:32:12.000Z","msg":